    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110330/extras/44d511b98d93b5b8df21cd9041c66163.poster.avif?t=1726684153\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110330/extras/44d511b98d93b5b8df21cd9041c66163.webm?t=1726684153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110330/extras/44d511b98d93b5b8df21cd9041c66163.mp4?t=1726684153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在 第九层 中，你发现自己被困在一个名为“Hotel Liminal”的神秘酒店里。为了逃脱，你必须在每一层找到异常。这些异常可能出现在任何地方——地面上、画中，甚至就在你眼前。你必须仔细检查每一个角落，因为一个错误就会把你送回开始的地方，即第九层。游戏为你提供了一种独特的恐怖氛围、解谜和生存体验，全都包裹在一个心理惊悚的体验中。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110330/extras/77d73c674a411add82c73f2651f5053b.poster.avif?t=1726684153\" width=610 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110330/extras/77d73c674a411add82c73f2651f5053b.webm?t=1726684153\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3110330/extras/77d73c674a411add82c73f2651f5053b.mp4?t=1726684153\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主要特点</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>探索神秘且富有氛围的酒店环境<br></li><li>在每一层发现有趣的异常<br></li><li>参与考验你的观察力和决策能力的挑战性游戏玩法<br></li><li>沉浸在恐怖的声音设计中</li></ul>",
